---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../../styles/article.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="AMS Eval - Privacy Policy — jtdub.com" description="Privacy policy for the AMS Eval app.">
  <article class="article">
    <div class="article__body" style="max-width: var(--measure); margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-9) var(--gutter) var(--space-10);">
<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h1>AMS Eval &mdash; Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">Last updated: March 10, 2026</p>

            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>AMS Eval is designed for monitoring Acute Mountain Sickness in remote, high-altitude environments. Your health data stays on your device and under your control.</p>

            <h2>Data Collection</h2>
            <p>AMS Eval does <strong>not</strong> collect any personal data. Specifically:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>No analytics or tracking SDKs are included.</li>
                <li>No user accounts or sign-in are required.</li>
                <li>No data is transmitted to our servers or any third party.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Health Data</h2>
            <p>AMS Eval records Lake Louise Score assessments, which may include symptom scores and severity classifications. This health-related data is:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Stored locally on your device.</li>
                <li>Never transmitted to external servers without your explicit action.</li>
                <li>Synced across your own devices via Apple CloudKit when connectivity is available.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>CloudKit sync uses your personal iCloud account and is encrypted by Apple. We do not have access to your iCloud data.</p>

            <h2>Location Data</h2>
            <p>The app uses GPS and barometric pressure to determine altitude for assessment context. Location and altitude data is stored locally and is not shared with any third party.</p>

            <h2>Person Data</h2>
            <p>Names or identifiers entered for tracked individuals are stored locally on your device and synced only via your personal iCloud account. We do not have access to this information.</p>

            <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>AMS Eval does not integrate with any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. The only external service used is Apple CloudKit for optional device-to-device sync via your personal iCloud account.</p>

            <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. Since no personal data is collected by us, the app is safe for users of all ages.</p>

            <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please visit the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a> or open an issue on the <a href="https://github.com/jtdub/ams-eval-app/issues" target="_blank">feedback repository</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
